彼得·弗兰普顿称奥兹·奥斯本为摇滚乐界的“贝蒂·怀特” https://www.nme.com/news/music/peter-frampton-calls-ozzy-osbourne-the-betty-white-of-rock-music-3749970?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=peter-frampton-calls-奥兹奥斯本贝蒂怀特摇滚音乐Surej SinghWed, 24 Apr 2024 08:11:54 +0000 Music NewsNewsMetalRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3749970 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/peter-frampton-ozzy-osbourne@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/peter-frampton-ozzy-osbourne@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/peter-frampton-ozzy-osbourne@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/peter-frampton-ozzy-osbourne@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/peter-frampton-ozzy-osbourne@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/peter-frampton-ozzy-osbourne@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/peter-frampton-ozzy-osbourne@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>他还表示与奥斯本一起表演“疯狂火车”将是“非常棒的”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/peter-frampton-calls-ozzy-osbourne-the-betty-white-of-rock-music-3749970">彼得·弗兰普顿 (Peter Frampton) 称奥兹·奥斯本 (Ozzy Osbourne) 为“摇滚音乐界的贝蒂·怀特 (Betty White)”，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/peter-frampton-ozzy-osbourne@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/peter-frampton-ozzy-osbourne@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/peter-frampton-ozzy-osbourne@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/peter-frampton-ozzy-osbourne@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/peter-frampton-ozzy-osbourne@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/peter-frampton-ozzy-osbourne@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/peter-frampton-ozzy-osbourne@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/peter-frampton">彼得·弗兰普顿 (Peter Frampton)</a>分享了他对<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rock-roll-hall-of-fame-2024-ozzy-osbourne-cher-and-more-to-be-inducted-3749163">即将进入摇滚名人堂的</a>想法，并将<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ozzy-osbourne">奥兹·奥斯本 (Ozzy Osbourne)</a>比作<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/betty-white-dead-aged-99-3128188">贝蒂·怀特 (Betty White)</a> 。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>了解更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-rock-roll-hall-of-fame-dionne-warwick-tina-turner-foo-fighters-2879619">摇滚名人堂已变成博物馆。改变的时刻到了</a></strong></li></ul><p>继<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rock-roll-hall-of-fame-2024-ozzy-osbourne-cher-and-more-to-be-inducted-3749163">昨天有消息称弗兰普顿和奥斯本将于今年晚些时候入选摇滚名人堂后</a>，弗兰普顿向<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-features/peter-frampton-rock-hall-induction-1235008452/"><em>滚石杂志</em></a>谈到了这一荣誉。</p><p>当被问及奥兹的入职时，弗兰普顿将黑暗王子与贝蒂·怀特进行了比较，一致认为贝蒂·怀特是一个可爱的人物：“这个人就是摇滚乐界的贝蒂·怀特。”他还表示，如果他能和奥斯本一起表演《疯狂火车》，那就“太棒了”。</p><p>在聊天的其他地方，弗兰普顿告诉该刊物，当他得知自己入职的消息时，他感到很惊讶：“这是我从未预料到的。因为我很久以前就符合资格，所以我把它抛在了脑后。就像在我获得第一个格莱美奖之前，我的器乐唱片没有唱过一个音符。我想，‘哦，我已经结束了。我永远不会赢得格莱美奖。看看发生了什么。我获得了格莱美奖。这是因为我继续工作。我从未放弃过。我不断地回来做更多的事情，并且不断地巡演。我重新建立了一批现在数量庞大的追随者。” </p><figure id="attachment_3192333" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3192333" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3192333" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Peter-Frampton-performing-live.jpg" alt="彼得·弗兰普顿" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Peter-Frampton-performing-live.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Peter-Frampton-performing-live-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Peter-Frampton-performing-live-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Peter-Frampton-performing-live-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Peter-Frampton-performing-live-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Peter-Frampton-performing-live-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3192333" class="wp-caption-text">彼得·弗兰普顿.图片来源：丹尼尔·奈顿/盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>然后他谈到了 R&amp;B 和说唱艺术家的入选，并谈到了 Mary J. Blige 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/a-tribe-called-quest">A Tribe Called Quest</a> ：“也许它应该被称为音乐名人堂，而不是摇滚名人堂。他们现在有点陷入困境。但我同意，玛丽·J·布莱姬是一位令人难以置信的天才。他们绝对都值得加入。”</p><p>弗兰普顿还谈到了雪儿<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cher-hits-out-at-rock-roll-hall-of-fame-after-repeated-snubs-3559731">之前的公开声明，即她在受到冷落后不会参加就职典礼</a>：“哦，继续吧，雪儿！我们希望你在那里。没关系。看看我等了多久。我没有像你等那么久，但没关系。你现在进来了。你在！来吧，雪儿！”</p><p>今年入选的其他乐队包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dave-matthews-band">Dave Matthews Band</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/foreigner">Foreigner</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kool-the-gang">Kool &amp; The Gang</a> 。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jimmy-buffett">吉米·巴菲特</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mc5">MC5</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dionne-warwick">迪昂·沃里克</a>和诺曼·惠特菲尔德将获得音乐卓越奖，而亚历克西斯·科纳、约翰·梅奥尔和 Big Mama Thornton 将获得音乐影响力奖。娱乐制作人苏珊娜·德帕斯将获得艾哈迈德·厄特根奖。</p><p>上述所有名字都将于 10 月 19 日在克利夫兰举行的仪式上就职。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/peter-frampton-calls-ozzy-osbourne-the-betty-white-of-rock-music-3749970">彼得·弗兰普顿 (Peter Frampton) 称奥兹·奥斯本 (Ozzy Osbourne) 为“摇滚音乐界的贝蒂·怀特 (Betty White)”，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
